Every single time is the same story, when Fanni launch a new update; our programmer “Islam” goes to Mecca just to pray that everything goes fine.
Until now .. everything is perfect.

So
What is our latest news?
For our new update we are working on an incredible changes. You will be amazed!

*Firstly, now you can view and accept your issued bill before it’s officially confirmed.
So you can make sure that you are paying the same agreed amount to the handyman.

*No more postponing without your approval. Now the handyman can no more postpone any request ..until you approve to do so, all of these changes because we want to make sure that you are being served at the best time for you.

*What else ? .. Guess what?!
The service that you always wanted finally is here!!
Yes .. Mobile fix
The best mobile fixing service you would have now available on our app

This in addition to other changes.. no need to bother you with all other long details, but please make sure we work hard to tailor your experience at our app.
